n.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/rTSBzJpEvlBVr4iQVLQivxGxf-8=/0x0:1597x1428/320x0/filters:focal(0x0:1597x1428):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/22328742/twitter_communities.png 320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/FJEKAiV5T2fdJlwWowLK_2A_chs=/0x0:1597x1428/520x0/filters:focal(0x0:1597x1428):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/22328742/twitter_communities.png 520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/zCcfLM3CGjPtp5kNjLfKelNkvJw=/0x0:1597x1428/720x0/filters:focal(0x0:1597x1428):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/22328742/twitter_communities.png 720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/M9PLuHN-aLIC6ZDzlzh7k1hQS2A=/0x0:1597x1428/920x0/filters:focal(0x0:1597x1428):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/22328742/twitter_communities.png 920w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/zRmI9_OBfK1vmxrDFQ9tllOufrg=/0x0:1597x1428/1120x0/filters:focal(0x0:1597x1428):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/22328742/twitter_communities.png 1120w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/9NkfGR7Ow333dy9TLaBvSGcF3UQ=/0x0:1597x1428/1320x0/filters:focal(0x0:1597x1428):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/22328742/twitter_communities.png 1320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/yBglDWUm2pcZohRuON9he70_uw4=/0x0:1597x1428/1520x0/filters:focal(0x0:1597x1428):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/22328742/twitter_communities.png 1520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/7zqSqSA-7tP7z_pOO2MVKhTYz3s=/0x0:1597x1428/1720x0/filters:focal(0x0:1597x1428):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/22328742/twitter_communities.png 1720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/WBPGxCrL1v50Mz9kLhZMd8hF4wA=/0x0:1597x1428/1920x0/filters:focal(0x0:1597x1428):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/22328742/twitter_communities.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1221px) 846px, (min-width: 880px) calc(100vw - 334px), 100vw\" alt=\"\" data-upload-width=\"1597\" src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0RoS8dXIVj3oHE5pHF5d5tUFn3I=/0x0:1597x1428/1200x0/filters:focal(0x0:1597x1428):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/22328742/twitter_communities.png\"></picture></span></span><span><figcaption>Twitter’s mockup of its Communities feature.</figcaption><cite>Image: Twitter.</cite></span></figure><p id=\"ccH4m7\">Twitter also announced a new feature called Communities, which appear to be its take on something like Facebook Groups. People can create and join groups around specific interests — like cats or plants, Twitter suggests — allowing them to see more tweets focused on those topics. Groups have been a huge success for Facebook (and a huge moderation problem, too), and they could be a particularly helpful tool on Twitter, since the service’s open-ended nature can make it difficult for new users to get started on the platform.</p><p id=\"AXBJ5l\">There’s no timeline yet for when either of these features will launch. Twitter listed them as “what’s next” for its platform during a presentation for analysts and investors this afternoon.</p></div><div id=\"connatix-article-desktop\" data-concert-ads-name=\"connatix-article-desktop\"><hr><p><span>Featured Videos From The Verge</span></p><h2><cnx-span>DJI Mini 2 review: the best drone under $500</cnx-span></h2><div><cnx><cnx><cnx></cnx><cnx><cnx id=\"id_c8ee1614317791114\"><cnx></cnx><cnx><cnx></cnx><cnx><cnx><cnx><svg viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"><path d=\"M18 5.4L16.6 4 11 9.6 5.4 4 4 5.4 9.6 11 4 16.6 5.4 18l5.6-5.6 5.6 5.6 1.4-1.4-5.6-5.6z\"></path></svg></cnx><cnx></cnx></cnx></cnx></cnx><cnx></cnx><cnx><cnx><cnx><cnx><cnx><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 4v16l16-8z\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg></cnx><cnx><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M9 21H3V3h6v18zm12 0h-6V3h6v18z\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg></cnx></cnx><cnx></cnx></cnx></cnx></